<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>OTP Verification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7fc;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .header h1 {
      color: #4a90e2;
      font-size: 28px;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .otp-code {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .otp-box {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 15px 25px;
      border: 2px solid #4a90e2;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #e5f0fc;
      color: #4a90e2;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.6;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: block;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .cta-button a {
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      font-size: 16px;
      font-weight: bold;
      border-radius: 30px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s;
    }
    .cta-button a:hover {
      background-color: #357ab7;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>{{subject}}</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="message">
      <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
      <p>We’ve received a request to verify your identity. Please use the OTP below to complete the verification:</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="otp-code">
      <div class="otp-box">
        {{otp}}
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="message">
      <p>This OTP is valid for <strong>2 minutes</strong> and can only be used once. If you didn’t request this, please ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-button">
      <a href="{{verification_url}}">Verify Now</a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for using our service!</p>
      <p>If you need assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
